# HLAE 2.130.1 (2022-04-21T18:40Z)
- Included AfxHookSource 1.109.1 (2022-04-21T18:40Z).

## AfxHookSource 1.109.1 (2022-04-21T18:40Z)
- Vastly improved the HLAE mirv_streams entity detection capabilities. This is also reflected in the updated afx/wh.cfg, since it now no more needs wonky tampering with disabling fastpath.

IMPORTANT: Do not forget to update your own configs (e.g. wh related cfgs) that might still use wonky fastpath related settings, this is not required anymore for improved entity detection.  
You should REMOVE any of these from your configs: cl_modelfastpath 0; cl_tlucfastpath 0; cl_brushfastpath 0
